      "slug": "194kg-of-produce-transferred-to-rochdale-food-bank-following-pantry-closure",
      "excerpt": "Following the closure of Irene’s Pantry, 194kg of produce was transferred to Rochdale Food Bank by local residents. The community effort was acknowledged at St James.",
